name: Slymebiote
description:
This came out of an attempt to do a venom-style symbiote, but then drifted into slime and liquid latex, so... Slymebiote.

Slymebiote clothing has a tight-fitting latex-like appearance, add words like 'dripping' and increase the weight to get wierd effects.

Trained a mix of about 40 images for 30k. (Not counting the failed attempts and restarts.)

Works better in semi-realistic models.

Also available as a LoRA.
